Author: Treasurer
Title: [ANN][ICO] PEATCOIN - blockchain option for the supply of peat
Body: Peat is extracted by two methods: milled and lumpy. In your project, only the milling method is described. And what about lumps? The extraction of peat by the lump method is less dependent on the weather.

Author: realsector
Title: [ANN][ICO] PEATCOIN - blockchain option for the supply of peat
Body: https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/5a3d1fb1706df50001a4214d/5a6b0e206b6b4400016d3c0b_1.png  WWW.PEATCOIN.COM White Paper One Page  At the moment our project is under preparation. We really appreciate your opinion about it. We'd love to hear any opinions and suggestions.  PEATCOIN is a project aimed at financing enterprise of the real sector, which is successfully functioning  The purpose of the investment is scaling up and increase production capabilities of the existing enterprise.  The company "ECOPROM" (trademark "Torfyanaya polyana" site:www.ekoprom-ekt.com) was created in 2015 and today is the most modern and high-tech enterprise in Russia in the industry of peat extraction and processing. The company has the mining licence (peat) for 25 years on the “Chistoe” deposits. in the Ozernyi village of Rezhevsky district of Sverdlovsk region.  The company "ECOPROM" is the only Russian company that receive the certificate of the peat producers, and membership in the World Association of Peat Manufacturers  www.peatsociety.org. Was also fairly received recognition and recommendations from the Ural branch of the Russian Academy of Sciences.  It was invested more than 16 000 000 USD in this project . The company was built “from scratch” with all necessary infrastructure organization that includes road construction, extending transmission lines, construction of facilities, continuing with the acquisition of the latest and most modern equipment from Canada (PremierTech) and Finland (Suokone).  https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/5a3d1fb1706df50001a4214d/5a6b0e20dbaf340001e24257_3.JPG  The enterprise facilities allow to produce peat with a third of the “Chistoe” deposits that roughly corresponds to the 250 000 m3 of peat per year. This volume of production we expect to reach in 2018 (without additional investments). At the same time, if we uncover the entire area allotted for production, the annual volume of extracted peat can be increased up to 750 000 m3 .  To increase the volume of peat extraction with subsequent processing up to 750,000 m3 per year investments are required in the amount of 10 000 000$ .  For the purposes of the ICO will be released 17 500 000 PeatCoin tokens. PeatCoin is a derivative, provided by peat: 10 PTN = 1 m3 of peat. Every PtC owner will be able to exchange their tokens on the peat multiple of one cubic meter. TOKEN SALE TERMS  https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/5a3d1fb1706df50001a4214d/5a6b0ebdf9957b0001b69d02_3211.JPG  We invite Advisors to our team For further information and cooperation please contact us support@peatcoin.com  • Telegram • Facebook • WEB Page • Twitter

Author: realsector
Title: [ANN][ICO] PEATCOIN - blockchain option for the supply of peat
Body: Peatcoin (PTN) — blockchain option for the supply of peat, which is enriched with peat. PTN tokens can be exchanged for a corresponding volume of raw peat at a rate of 10 PTN per 1 m3 of peat (exchange will be held with minimum increments of 1 m3) immediately after ICO completion. Additionally, the economic model of our token assumes a procedure of bayback. We guarantee  tokens buy-back at the market price, but not below 1.6 $ per PTN. Buy-back within 5 years, amounting to 15.5 million $ More information is available on our website in the section Papers. Also you can visit our chat in the telegram  and ask all the questions.
